<!--BCI Colors-->
<!--
Note if any change is needed
Colors for the BCI layout has to be carefully selected since the colors need to have contrast between the background color and the highlighting color
foreground = animations colors 
highlightSelectedForeground = Edges colors

         background="#232433"                   IN USE BACKGROUND
         foreground="#ffaa00"                   IN USE ANIMATIONS
         highlightSelectedBackground="Black"    IN USE FOR STRINGS INSIDE BUTTONS 
         highlightSelectedForeground="#ffffff"  IN USE BORDERS AND IN USE FOR STRINGS INSIDE BUTTONS
         highlightBackground="#FFB100"
         highlightForeground="#C1C2D3"/>          IN USE PROGRESS BARS COLOR, TEXT BOX AND LABEL PROMPT


HighlightSelectedBackground and HighlightForeground need to be a contrast between this colors

-->


